title: To Yearn-5/10/15
author: Davey_Babey
pages:
#- Happy Mother's day!

Please take care of Oliver while I'm gone,
I'm worried about him...
He spends far too much time in the bar with those animals.

Be sure to have lots of fun while I'm gone!
#- In addition to mother's day, it's also my birthday, and I'm old now.
If you want to leave me for somebody younger I'll understand.

#- 